  <p style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;">Once you’ve done that:</p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 18px;">
    <li style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;"><%= link_to "Start building your page", my_chippd_pages_url %> using a mix of photos, video, audio, text, and other fun content.</li>
    <li style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;"><%= link_to('Download our app', go_url) %>. You’ll need it to view any page created on Chipp’d.</li>
    <li style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;">Read up on <%= link_to("how Chipp'd works", how_it_works_url) %> and check out <%= link_to('our FAQs', faq_url) %> for more information.</li>
