  <p style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: #444444; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif;">If you need to check on the status of your gift or have any questions at all, please contact us at <%= mail_to('orders@chippd.com') %>. We're always here for you.</p>

